            "pub_date": "2025-11-20 08:35:41",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港元拆息全跌　1個月拆息跌穿3厘　創約兩個半月新低",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15434998&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港元拆息全線向下，是近兩星期以來首次。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">短期拆息跌幅較大，隔夜拆息跌至1.622厘，單日跌約19點子，連跌4個交易日累計跌約1.07厘，創逾3個月新低。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">樓按相關的1個月拆息亦四連跌，跌穿3厘水平，報約2.878厘，單日跌約13點子，4日累計跌約24點子，創約兩個半月低位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">反映銀行資金成本的3個月拆息跌至3.416厘，跌約2點子，連跌3日。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，6個月及12個月拆息均跌至約3.368厘水平，同樣扭轉上日升勢。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15434998-%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e5%85%a8%e8%b7%8c%e3%80%801%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e8%b7%8c%e7%a9%bf3%e5%8e%98%e3%80%80%e5%89%b5%e7%b4%84%e5%85%a9%e5%80%8b%e5%8d%8a%e6%9c%88-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source_licensed_HKD_shutterstock-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-20 08:35:44",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "和鉑醫藥與輝瑞訂立非獨家授權協議",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">和鉑醫藥(02142)公布，與輝瑞訂立非獨家授權協議，旨在推進針對多種潛在疾病適應症的臨床前抗體發現工作。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/01/20240131_FI_source-ap_輝瑞_Pfizer.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/01/20240131_FI_source-ap_輝瑞_Pfizer.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據協議條款，輝瑞將獲得和鉑醫藥旗下諾納生物專有HCAb平台的全球使用權，以開發全人源僅重鏈抗體。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">諾納生物將獲得首付款，並有權獲得監管、臨床及商業里程碑付款。此外，諾納生物可與輝瑞合作，利用諾納生物的HCAb平台、先進的B細胞篩選技術及綜合服務開展抗體發現、開發及工程。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15441063-%e5%92%8c%e9%89%91%e9%86%ab%e8%97%a5%e8%88%87%e8%bc%9d%e7%91%9e%e8%a8%82%e7%ab%8b%e9%9d%9e%e7%8d%a8%e5%ae%b6%e6%8e%88%e6%ac%8a%e5%8d%94%e8%ad%b0",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/02142-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-20 08:35:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "萬國數據上季扭虧為盈 經調整EBITDA按年升11.4%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">萬國數據(09698)公布，今年第3季扭虧為盈，錄得淨利潤7.29億元(人民幣．下同)；去年同期則有淨虧損2.31億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"萬國數據官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/GDS.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"萬國數據官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/GDS.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">萬國數據官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內淨收入28.87億元，按年增長10.2%。按非公認會計準則的經調整EBITDA達13.42億元，按年也升11.4%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司主席兼首席執行官黃偉先生表示，公司在上季持續交付積壓訂單，並實現高遷入率。現已做好充分的戰略準備以把握AI領域日益增長的需求，將AI視為業務長期增長的重要催化劑。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15441047-%e8%90%ac%e5%9c%8b%e6%95%b8%e6%93%9a%e4%b8%8a%e5%ad%a3%e6%89%ad%e8%99%a7%e7%82%ba%e7%9b%88-%e7%b6%93%e8%aa%bf%e6%95%b4ebitda%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%8711-4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/09698-2024.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-20 08:30:30",
